        <p class="faq-answer mt-2 text-xs sm:text-sm text-body leading-relaxed pl-1">
          Grammarly AI Humanizer is the best free AI humanizer tool. It offers free access that allows users to instantly convert robotic text into natural human writing. Users can bypass major detectors without signing up for expensive monthly plans, making it the top choice for students, bloggers, and freelance content creators.
        </p>
